nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 129 is the 107th issue of the magazine Star Wars Insider and the 37th published by Titan Magazines. It was released on October 25, 2011.

James Arnold Taylor on being the voice of Republic hero Obi-Wan Kenobi! We go beneath the waves as Insider takes the plunge to meet the warriors under the surface. Why Star Wars' fringe characters make all the difference! Plus, makeup master and Oscar winner Dave Elsey on recreating Chewbacca!
